high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter
Pick up the lotion bottle from the counter
Turn around and take a step then turn to the right and take a few steps then turn to the right again
Open the cupboard under the sink and put the lotion bottle inside
Turn left and go to the wall then turn left and go to the garbage can
Get the lotion bottle from the garbage can
Turn around and head to the toilet then turn right then left and face the counter
Put the lotion bottle in the cupboard under the sink
anns.task_desc: Put two lotion bottles in the cupboard under the sink

high_descs: Turn left to face the right side of the sink.
Pick up the bottle of lotion to the left of the toilet paper.
Turn left and move to the left side of the sink, look at the bottom cabinets.
Open the cabinet on the right side, place the lotion in the cabinet, close the cabinet.
Turn left and walk to the right side of the tub facing the black bin on the floor.
Pick up the hand lotion that's in the black bin.
Turn and walk back to the left side of the sink looking at the cabinets below.
Open the cabinet below the sink on the right side and place the bottle of lotion behind the first bottle.
anns.task_desc: To move two bottles of lotion to the cabinet.

high_descs: Walk forward slightly then turn and face the left at the counter
Pick up the soap dispenser bottle from the counter
Turn to the left and walk straight slightly then turn right and face the counter
Open the bottom right cabinet door and place the soap inside then close the door
Turn to the left walk forward slightly then turn left and walk towards the black trash bin
Pick up the soap bottle from the inside of the trash bin
Turn left and walk straight slightly then turn to the left and face the counter
Open the bottom right cabinet door and place the soap inside then close the door
anns.task_desc: Putting soap dispenser bottles in the cabinet
